WEBVTT

00:00:58.115 --> 00:01:00.985
The same profile in the US,

00:01:01.009 --> 00:01:06.342
despite a momentary rebound 15 years ago,

00:01:06.366 --> 00:01:09.730
and despite all
the technological innovations

00:01:09.754 --> 00:01:12.333
around us: the Internet, the information,

00:01:12.357 --> 00:01:15.578
the new information
and communication technologies.

00:01:16.155 --> 00:01:20.734
When productivity grows
three percent per annum,

00:01:20.758 --> 00:01:24.400
you double the standard of living
every generation.

00:01:25.169 --> 00:01:30.178
Every generation is twice
as well-off as its parents'.